    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - IC BUS SERVICE MANUAL - OPERATION - DRIVER'S CONSOLE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="1">
        <title>DRIVER'S CONSOLE</title>
        <para>The driver's console (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700105">Figure 5</hotlnk>) is located on the left side, center, and to the right of the
            steering wheel. A switch located on the driver's console or the dash operates all body options. On school
            buses equipped with an air actuated entrance door, the air door control switch is located to the left or
            right of the steering wheel, depending on the various state requirements.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700105" figsize="col-wide">
